# 🌱 Green Technology Marketplace

A web-based marketplace platform focused on green and sustainable technology products.  
This project is created for **testing and learning purposes** and is hosted using **Firebase Hosting** with **Firebase Database**.

---

## 🚀 Features

- User authentication (Customer / Vendor / Admin)
- Customer dashboard
- Vendor dashboard
- Product listing
- Firebase database integration
- Responsive UI
- Hosted with Firebase (HTTPS enabled)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Backend / Database:** Firebase
- **Hosting:** Firebase Hosting

---

